  schema:name "Lynn Trefzger";
  schema:description """Lynn's versatile comedy talent brings her many characters to life, including a silly but lovable camel, a grumpy old man, a feisty little girl, and even audience volunteers. Her interactive performances are tailored for family and adult audiences, ensuring a unique and hilarious experience every time.
