iwts_performer:1209 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Backyard Betties";
  schema:description "Backyard Betties is a lively, fiddle-driven trio blending country, folk, and roots with heart, humour, and energy. With rich harmonies, standout fiddle, and a relaxed vibe, their shows feel like a night out with friends. Nancy’s warm, quick-witted banter brings people together, turning audiences into part of the experience. From toe-tapping tunes to singalongs, they create a fun, welcoming atmosphere. Fully self-contained and easy to host, delivering a seamless, all-inclusive show. Perfect for community and theatre audiences.";
