iwts_performer:1578 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "The Second City Touring Company";
  schema:description "The Second City performs social satire through scripted scenes, improvisation and music.  Their alumni list is a \"Who's Who\" this legendary theater has trained for decades:  John Belushi, Martin Short, Catherine O'Hara, Jason Sudeikis, Bill Murray, Adam McKay, Tina Fey, Steve Carell, Amy Poehler, Stephen Colbert, Keegan-Michael Key, Bob Odenkirk, and hundreds more.   “A Temple of Satire” - TIME   Multiple shows available every season including a holiday show.   Workshops in theatrical and applied improv are a must.  Easy to produce and funny!";
