  schema:description "I am one of two Performer/Creator/Producers of the hit show, \"How We Got To Jersey\", which Jeff Madden and I have toured all over Ontario to rave reviews and sold-out crowds.   Jeff and I are both international stage performers with 20 years of experience wowing audiences with our stories and songs, and in \"How We Got To Jersey\", we take you behind the scenes of the hit musical JERSEY BOYS to learn how a couple of small-town boys from Canada made it big all around the world playing Frankie Valli.";
