iwts_performer:2568 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "BONNIE";
  schema:description """Bonnie Kilroe was born and raised in Vancouver, BC. She attended Studio 58 before heading out on her own to carve her own path in musical theatre and cabaret. Necessity is the mother of invention and that is exactly how her career began combining her love of singing, impersonating and comedy.
She has a natural ability to make her audience feel taken care of, at home and totally at ease. 
This makes it easier to get audience members on stage with her throughout the show leading to some of the most hilarious show segments.""";
