  schema:description "Matt Zaddy is a Mississauga singer?songwriter and award?winning musician whose folk-rock, soul, and Americana blend with heartfelt storytelling. His music explores life, love, loss, and hope, earning international airplay and wide streaming reach. A dedicated community arts advocate, he mentors emerging artists and creates inclusive spaces that support local music culture.";
