iwts_performer:4300 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Amanda Martinez";
  schema:description """Amanda Martinez has been embraced by audiences all over the world with five highly acclaimed albums to her credit: Sola, Amor, Mañana, Libre, and, most recently, Recuerdo.

Accompanied by her band of 20 years, Amanda Martinez has sold out Ottawa’s National Arts Centre and Toronto’s Koerner Hall and Winter Garden Theatres. 

She has performed internationally, including at the Dubai International Jazz Festival, the 2010 FIFA World Cup Festivities in South Africa, the Pan-American Games in Guadalajara and at New York City’s Blue Note Jazz Club.""";
