  schema:name "Shades of Bublé: A Three-Man Tribute to Michael Bublé";
  schema:description "SHADES OF BUBLÉ: A Three-Man Tribute to Michael Bublé brings the swinging standards and pop hits of Michael Bublé to the stage in an unforgettable concert event. This act consistently wows audiences around the country with exciting harmonies and smooth choreography, combining big-band standards from the jazz era, classic hits from the 50s/60s/70s, as well as Billboard hits from today in a high-energy show that generates standing ovations from sold-out crowds. SHADES OF BUBLÉ is a one-of-a-kind headliner show perfect for audiences of all ages!";
