  schema:name "Jaedyn Tributes and The Flashback Band";
  schema:description "Jaedyn Pilon is an award-winning tribute artist known for his authentic performances and high-energy entertainment. Whether capturing the charisma of Elvis Presley or the deep storytelling of Johnny Cash, he mesmerizes audiences with powerful vocals and electrifying stage presence. Backed by top-tier musicians, including the nine-piece Flashback band, Jaedyn delivers a nostalgic yet thrilling experience. Performing across Canada in theaters, festivals, and Legions, he brings legendary music to life with passion and precision.";
