iwts_performer:4648 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Gwen & The Hitmakers";
  schema:description """Gwen Hughes & The Hitmakers have been making music together for over two decades.  Gwen Hughes leads the popular Southeast band THE RETRO KATS (specializing in early 1900-1930s music) and THE CONTINENTAL DANCE ORHCESTRA, which plays classic big band and jazz. The historical nature of THE HITMAKERS makes it a natural extension of those bands & uses many of the same players.

Vocalist Gwen Hughes has  over 30 years of performances to her credit - including 10 years touring in Europe - and is a memorable performer.   \"The audience comes first.\"""";
