iwts_performer:4655 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Heather Massie";
  schema:description "Heather Massie is a Fulbright Specialist & NYC actor/playwright/producer. She tours the world with her 31x award-winning, internationally acclaimed solo show, HEDY! The Life & Inventions of Hedy Lamarr, which she premiered Off-Broadway in 2016 and has since toured thru 26 countries on 5 continents. She has always been fascinated by science and studied Astrophysics and Theatre Arts. She has been sponsored by several US Embassies and served as a Fulbright Specialist to South Africa in 2019 and to Australia in 2024 through the US State Department.";
