  schema:name "Antonio";
  schema:description "Antonio Rocha (pronounced Haw-sha) is an internationally renowned  and award wining  solo performer. Using his unique fusion of mime and verbal narratives, his tenor voice and realistic sound effects,  he brings original and adapted stories  to life in a captivating and Educational  way. Rocha's  career spans 40 years with performances in  20 countries on 6 continents and 44 US states. Some highlights include  The Kennedy Center, The Smithsonian, Wolf Trap,  and various other events such as festivals, museums and educational institutions.";
