iwts_performer:5786 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Emily Asher's Garden Party";
  schema:description """Emily Asher is a trombonist, singer, educator, bandleader, & songwriter. The New York Times notes her “buoyant charm” and Wall Street Journal claims “In traditional jazz, the trombone comes closest to the human voice, although up to now it's rarely been cast as a distinctly female voice… Ms. Asher plays with both grit and grace”  
Asher and her uncommonly versatile New York City-based band play hot jazz, swing, and latin originals ranging from striking and unusual to traditional and catchy, taking listeners on a fun international sound tour.""";
