iwts_performer:5790 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "The McDades";
  schema:description """Punching through the walls of tradition, The McDades’ Celtic-rooted music fuses the spontaneity of jazz improvisation and infectious global rhythms. The Juno Award winners’ cutting edge sound is the perfect complement to their fiery performances. This compelling and dynamic group “finds their groove somewhere between a down-home kitchen party, a jazzy after hours club, and a folk festival.”(London Free Press)
The McDades are winners of a Juno Award and 3 Canadian folk music awards and are excited to be releasing \"Thread The Light” Apr ‘26.""";
