iwts_performer:5820 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Buzz Brass";
  schema:description "Featuring fresh musical arrangements in a unique repertoire that brilliantly blends classical music and various styles, combined with a strong stage presence that appeals to a wide audience, Buzz Brass is one of the most renowned brass quintets in Canada. Since 2002, the ensemble has presented over 2000 concerts, reaching over 500 000 music lovers across North America, Europe, Colombia and China. In 2025-26, more than 100 concerts were presented across Canada and the United States, a great success for this “top-notch brass quintet” (CBC Music).";
