iwts_performer:5868 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Von Bieker";
  schema:description """Von Bieker plays indie-folk that haunts your heart with small stories, big questions and vintage bowties.

His thoughtful lyrics, emotional performances and sharp wit have gathered fans seeking connection. His album DUMB HOPE reached #45 on CKUA radio’s Top 100 Albums of 2024 and #6 on the national !Earshot Folk/Roots/Blues chart.

Based in Edmonton, Von Bieker’s influences range from the guitar-grooves of Bahamas to the spiritual depth of Bruce Cockburn; the breaking-point passion of Glen Hansard to the quirky joy of the Talking Heads.""";
  schema:url <https://vonbieker.com>;
