iwts_performer:6354 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Rube & Rake";
  schema:description """Rube & Rake engage audiences with a mixture of stories, intricate guitar work, and rich vocal harmonies. After working together for the past 7 years out of St. John's, NL, Josh Sandu and Andrew Laite have fused an intimate musical connection that comes across in every new song and performance.

ECMA 2022 Songwriter of the Year, Rube & Rake's music is an exercise in creating something beyond the sum of their parts. Their upcoming full-length album titled Good Times After Bad, will be released on May 9, 2025.""";
