iwts_performer:6755 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Gwen Hughes & The Retro Kats";
  schema:description """Atlanta icons Gwen Hughes & Ruby Reds join forces to create “Gwen Hughes & The Retro Kats.”
The Ruby Reds Band is the longest tenured jazz band in Georgia. The band was formed in early 1966 to perform nightly at a rowdy beer hall called Ruby Reds Warehouse in  Atlanta, Georgia and has been playing constantly ever since.

An international touring artist, Gwen Hughes has crooned from Stockholm to Istanbul in partnership with the US State Dept.  Gwen leads the variety band, THE ‘KATS & classic swing big band, THE CONTINENTAL DANCE ORCHESTRA.""";
  schema:url <https://alkahestartists.net/www/artists/gwen-hughes---the-retro-kats/80>;
  schema:knowsAbout <http://kg.artsdata.ca/resource/MusicPerformance>;
  schema:genre "Jazz/Blues";
