iwts_performer:7350 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Dr. Daylight's Jazz Company";
  schema:description "“If Frank Sinatra hung out in New Orleans...” Grab your white handkerchiefs and parasols, and get ready for a second-line parade! Dr. Daylight’s Jazz Company engages crowds with its rich, energetic shows.  Crooner Spencer Racca fronts the Company and thrills crowds with his Dean Martin, Frank Sinatra, and Elvis Presley vocal stylings. Most recently, multi-lingual vocalist Ashley Orlando joined the Company and delights audiences with French renditions of American Songbook classics.";
