  schema:name "Scarlett Butler";
  schema:description """Scarlett Butler is a new Canadian music duo comprised of SOCAN Award-winners, Troy Kokol and Joni Delaurier. But ask anyone in the Canadian country music industry and they would be known better individually for crafting songs you have probably heard on the radio.

The pair formed Scarlett Butler in 2020 and came onto the scene in unconventional style writing, producing, and releasing the Billboard Top 50 song “Looking for a Lockdown with You”.  The duo are working on a new album slated for release in 2025.""";
