  schema:name "Last Birds";
  schema:description "Last Birds is the offspring of Saskatchewan Country Music Award winners Lindsay Arnold and Mike Davis. Using their small prairie hometown as a backdrop, Last Birds weave together rural legends and current day experiences to form a modern prairie gothic. Their two voices-two guitars approach is steeped in early country folk influence and provides an intimate storytelling experience audiences have repeatedly described as mesmerizing.";
