  schema:description "High energy R&B/Soul/Pop a cappella that’ll have you singing, dancing, and even beatboxing along! Ball in the House has performed everywhere - from theaters to colleges to fairs & festivals - and has been inspiring students with their nationally recognized educational outreach for over 25 years. As featured on The TODAY Show and America's Got Talent, and having opened for some of the biggest artists in the world (The Jonas Brothers, The Temptations), they guarantee a fantastic experience!";
