iwts_performer:7670 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Munro & Patrick";
  schema:description "\"The Duo\"- As a sought after & awarded, seasoned duo from Saskatchewan, their performances and songs are rich with the aroma of confidence, that comes with years of perfecting a most delectable & inviting recipe' for their audience. It makes you want to sit right down at their table & partake. A Munro & Patrick performance is your favorite simmering dish, infused with deep flavors of rockin' blues, the spice of jazz, the warmth of traditional country, the soul of RnB, the earthiness of folk, sprinkled with the sweet nostalgia of Motown. Enjoy.";
