  schema:name "Kitchen Sink Pocket Orchestra";
  schema:description "Kitchen Sink Pocket Orchestra is a mixed string and wind quartet designed to introduce orchestral instruments in accessible and non-traditional settings. Their diverse repertoire appeals to audiences of all ages and includes arrangements of much loved orchestral works, mashups of traditional folk and fiddle favorites alongside recognizable tunes from contemporary artists including Lady Gaga, The Beatles, and Metallica and more-that and the Kitchen Sink.";
