iwts_performer:7726 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "The Leading Ladies";
  schema:description """Taking cues from the vintage stylings of the 1940s, 50s, and 60s, the Leading Ladies blend beloved jazz and blues classics with fresh, original arrangements and a high-energy, swingin' performance style. 

Directed by trombonist Casey Thomas-Burns, this dynamic and vibrant group of women have toured the province numerous times from their home base of Vancouver for festivals, concert tours, and educational tours- with over 40 performance in 2024 alone.""";
