  schema:name "Aaron MacDonald";
  schema:description "Aaron MacDonald is a Cape Breton troubadour with a country heart and rock ’n’ roll grit. His songs draw from working life, family, and small-town roots, delivered with raw honesty and hook-heavy melodies. A proven draw who regularly sells out Halifax’s Carleton, Aaron has built a reputation for turning real stories into anthems that stick long after the last chord rings out.";
