  schema:name "Daniel Duggan";
  schema:description "Daniel Duggan, an expert percussionist and successful touring performer with years of professional success in Canada & UK. Original holder of the Official Guinness Worlds Record for the Largest Djembe Drum Ensemble. A Scottish artist of African descent with roots in the Caribbean and South America. His artistry reflects his rich cultural roots. His performances overflow with his passion for percussion & people. Audiences love the interactive cultural experiences that combine; drums, energy & creativity to empower individuals & release joy.";
  schema:url <http://www.rhythm-resource.com>;
