  schema:name "Mr Mark";
  schema:description "Mark Cameron, known as “Mr. Mark,” is a Canadian performer, composer, and creator of theatrical work for young audiences. Since 2002, he has toured extensively across Canada and performed at major festivals. A longtime collaborator with the Winnipeg Symphony Orchestra, his original symphonic works have also been presented by the Regina Symphony Orchestra and Symphony New Brunswick.";
