iwts_performer:7956 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Adria Jackson";
  schema:description "Celtic singing harpist, Adria Jackson,  skillfully performs traditional Celtic/Maritime songs, originals & folk inspired classical songs reminiscent of Loreena McKennitt and early Joni Mitchell.   This spring she toured Barcelona, UK, Vancouver & Niagara Falls.  She has released two albums: Troubadour(2023) and Helen Creighton & The Songs of the Red Parlour (2025).  Performance highlights: Atlantic Film Festival, Harmony Bazaar Festival, Government House(NS), The Osprey Arts Centre, Helen Creighton Folk Club & The Sanctuary Arts Centre.";
