  schema:description "Founded in 2005 by a group of competitive skaters determined to break free from the world of sparkles and medals, Le Patin Libre has forged a bold new approach to contemporary performance. Their work has earned critical acclaim and captivated audiences across major arts festivals, national stages, and international tours. Defined by speed, virtuosity, and seamless ensemble choreography, Le Patin Libre’s style is both sophisticated and accessible—delighting, provoking, and inspiring in equal measure.";
