  schema:description "Carrie Marshall is a blend of pop, soul, folk and jazz with singer-songwriter sensibilities.  Known for  expressive, warm vocals, piano-driven melodies, and emotionally rich storytelling, Carrie seamlessly blends styles in her genre-bending shows. Carrie curates several themed shows that resonate with broad audiences, bringing  soul and spirit of jazz improvisation to new listeners through popular and original music. Carrie tours with a band ranging from a quintet to septet ensemble.";
