  schema:name "Timothy Noel";
  schema:description "Timothy Noel & The RearViews are an Edmonton-based powerhouse delivering a high-octane blend of Motown, Soul and classics. Fronted by the charismatic Timothy Noel, this ensemble features a driving rhythm section and a signature blazing horn line that bridges classic soul nostalgia with modern energy. Known for immersive live experiences and world-class musicianship, the band celebrates the legacies of Marvin Gaye and Stevie Wonder while pushing the boundaries of contemporary groove with infectious, soulful joy on every stage.";
