iwts_performer:8326 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Jeki Yoo";
  schema:description "Over 13 million people watched Korean magician JEKI YOO wow the judges on America’s Got Talent. After this appearance he was dubbed “The Cutest Magician ever!”  From the Edinburg Festival to Penn and Teller’s Fool US; Jeki's multi award winning comedy magic show travels the world with his family friendly show. His full show includes his magician wife Ellie with their Guinness Book World Record holding quick-change routine. He is multi-lingual, resides in the US with a green card.";
