iwts_performer:8339 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Theresa Thor";
  schema:description """Theresa Thordarson’s boundless creative drive springs from a lifetime of musical risk-taking.

Growing up in rural Manitoba, Theresa experienced an environment where the classical canon was just one of many influences. Her curiosity has led her to explore unexpected connections across musical worlds as a pianist, vocalist, composer and collaborator.  Her creations embrace playful pastoral poetry, subtle and surprising harmonies, and memorable melodies.

Theresa makes her home in Winnipeg, Manitoba where she hosts a lively teaching studio.""";
