  schema:name "Sonia Deleo";
  schema:description "Sonia Deleo is an award-winning singer/songwriter, a comedian, a playwright and an actor. Her folk-soul sound and engaging storytelling make her performances a rich and impactful experience for audiences of all kinds. With two solo albums, one musical, and several singles and collaborations under her belt, Deleo is a force in the Canadian music scene and she is only gaining momentum. With a dynamic vocal range, intricately woven lyrics, and unique melodies, her music stands out in a vast sea of sounds.";
