  schema:name "Every Brilliant Thing";
  schema:description "Our award-winning hit comedy about depression & gratitude featuring Elizabeth Nepjuk. Since 2018 we’ve brought this life-altering hilarious solo show that boosts emotional wellbeing & busts mental health stigma to over 8000 people through 152 performances in 27 cities spread from Langley, BC to Moosoomin, SK. Burnt Thicket Theatre has inspired 30,300+ people in 59 cities from Halifax to Victoria through 37 professional productions, 22 world premieres of new Canadian plays, 2 national tours, 6 western Canada tours & 6 provincial tours (AB & SK).";
