iwts_performer:8386 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Champagne Weather";
  schema:description """Champagne Weather is new music from James Hill and Anne Janelle. Separately and together, Hill and Janelle have won a CFMA and garnered both JUNO and ECMA nominations. They have performed at venues and festivals across Canada and internationally from New York to Tokyo to London. With Champagne Weather, the duo shows their musical breadth creating \"the future of folk music.\" (Ian Tamblyn)

Champagne Weather makes time stand still. Every song is a shimmering blanket of sound with flashes of Philip Glass, Appalachian fiddle and Maritime folksong.""";
