iwts_performer:8403 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Suzie Ungerleider";
  schema:description """Suzie Ungerleider’s gloriously emotive, crystalline voice and bewitching performances have captivated audiences for over 25 years. She began performing as Oh Susanna in the mid-1990s, earning praise for her striking voice and poetic songcraft.

A wordsmith with a keen mind for detail and a wicked sense of humour, her songs and voice pierce the heart, inspire a knowing laugh or a welling of the eye. Her music criss-crosses Americana, folk, and roots. A Genie and CFMA winner with 3 JUNO nominations, she now lives in Vancouver with her family.""";
  schema:url <https://www.suzieungerleider.com>;
