iwts_performer:8469 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "LittleFox";
  schema:description """Featuring the original songs of singer/multi-instrumentalist Alison Jenkins, LittleFox's thoughtful original songs are about love, death, longing, belonging, and finding your way in strange times. 
Her first EP, Desire Lines, was released in 2022; her second EP, Ghost In This House, was released in May 2023. A single, Vesuvius, followed in May 2024. Her next EP, will be released in the summer of 2025. 
LittleFox is equally mesmerizing as a 1-piece solo act or a 9-piece \"large band\" complete with string section.""";
