iwts_performer:8546 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Ira Pettle";
  schema:description """Inspired by, A Little Bit, an album co-written with Juno award winner, Norman Foote, Ira’s newest production, A Little Bit Live! puts his love of storytelling and song into a musical theatre experience for young audiences.  

Originally trained as an actor, Ira is a key player in BC’s arts scene, most notably in Whistler. Known as ‘DJ Ira’ throughout the Sea to Sky corridor, he is one of Canada’s most sought-after family entertainers and this next chapter of his life’s work is sure to make a big splash across multi-generational audiences.""";
