  schema:name "Brother Bicker Band";
  schema:description "For over a decade, the seven piece Calgary-based Brother Bicker Band has been captivating and converting audiences with their raw energy, seasoned musicianship, beautiful harmonies and undeniable chemistry on stage. They are self-described ‘Maple Whiskey Rock n’ Roll’, striking a chord somewhere between nostalgic and new; with influences from Tom Petty, Fleetwood Mac and The Black Crowes and carving out a sound that is entirely their own.";
