  schema:name "Andrew Moore Trio";
  schema:description "The Andrew Moore Trio is a blues rock band from Moncton, New Brunswick, led by guitarist and songwriter Andrew Moore with Jake Leger on bass and Jeremy Hebert on drums. Their sound blends the weight of blues and the edge of rock, drawing influence from The Black Keys and Stevie Ray Vaughan. Known for their high-energy performances, the trio has appeared at festivals including Harvest, Paddlefest, and Dooryard.";
