  schema:description "ADEOLUWA is an experimental Afro-fusion artist blending influences from Adekunle Gold, Stephen Schwartz, and more. Featured in CBC, Pulse.ng, and others, his music has aired on CBC Radio, CJTR, and City 105.1FM. A Saskatchewan Music Awards nominee, he’s collaborated with artists like Melodna and performed at venues like Amigos Cantina. ADEOLUWA delivers unforgettable live shows, connecting hearts through music that transcends genres.";
