iwts_performer:8706 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Rev Dave";
  schema:description "Rev Dave is a singer-songwriter who has written nearly 300 songs in the Americana vein.  He is front-person for the band, Rev Dave and the Sin Eaters. Since their first album in 2020, Rev Dave’s tunes have led the Sin Eaters to three Music NL nominations for Folk/ Roots Artist of the year and Country Artist ofd the Year, as well as,  two ECMA nominations for the album Beams of Love, which was nominated in both the Blues and Country Categories. Toe-tapping rhythms and thoughtful, playful and poetic lyrics are hallmarks of his songs.";
