  schema:name "Joselyn & Don";
  schema:description """Montana-raised, Los Angeles-based duo Joselyn & Don blend Laurel Canyon folk, soul, and classic Americana with a cinematic edge. Their third album \"Lost & Found Highway\" has earned international radio play and critical praise for Joselyn’s \"singular voice” and Don’s “skilled fingerpicking,” and spent ten weeks on Americana radio’s Top 100. 
