  schema:name "JUAN PEREZ RODRIGUEZ";
  schema:description """Imagine stepping into a world shaped by the artistry of Juan Pérez \"Aure.\" Direct from Spain, this celebrated 
pianist \"Flamenco Composer of the Year\" is ready to share his newest project\", SOMA, with you.  

With his genre-bending arrangements and remarkable virtuosity with SOMA, Aure blends passion and contemporary style and creates a thrilling musical journey that will leave you excited and inspired for more.

We'll witness Auxi Fernandez weave stories of passion, sorrow, and transcendence.""";
