  schema:name "Queen City Cabaret";
  schema:description """Queen City Cabaret is a Cincinnati-based arts organization and musical duo that brings captivating performances of vintage jazz and pop to venues across the country.

Founded by professional musicians (and friends!) Sarah Folsom and Matthew Umphreys in 2018, QCC celebrates the beloved songs and stories of 20th century American commercial music with expertly-curated intimate cabarets, large-scale concerts, and everything in between.""";
