  schema:name "Queenz That Rock";
  schema:description """Queenz That Rock- Unleashing Rock Royalty 
Three powerhouse women bring the house down with an electrifying mix of rock's greatest hits from legendary male and female artists. From the raw energy of Pat Benatar and Heart to the anthems of Bon Jovi, Fleetwood Mac, Bob Segar, Tina Turner, and the iconic Janis Joplin, Queenz delivers a night of pure rock madness that will leave you wanting more!""";
