iwts_performer:8910 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Eagle Wings & More";
  schema:description """Get Ready for the Ultimate Musical Experience!
A high-energy show featuring the greatest hits from the most iconic songwriters in music history. Look no further than “Eagle Wings & More with End Of The Innocence”!

The setlist is a treasure trove of chart-topping, Grammy award-winning hits from the likes of:
Don Henley
Paul McCartney
Neil Diamond
Dan Fogelberg
Glenn Frey
Kenny Loggins
The Eagles

“Eagle Wings & More with End Of The Innocence\" is the ultimate tribute to the songwriters who shaped the music landscape.""";
