  schema:name "Honky Tonk Chicks";
  schema:description "Honky Tonk Chicks are known for their show-stopping live performances and captivate audiences with tight harmonies, dynamic choreography, and unmatched entertainment value. Equal parts throwback and fresh, they fuse timeless country roots with a bold, modern edge—creating a high-octane experience that keeps audiences singing, dancing, and wanting more. Their star power is so bright, it landed them on Netflix's \"Star Search.\"";
