iwts_performer:9012 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Teagan Littlechief";
  schema:description "Teagan Littlechief  a powerhouse country rock artist from Saskatchewan, renowned for dynamic vocals and a commanding stage presence. Earning her many accolades, including the 2024 SCMA Female Artist of the Year, 3x SCMA Indigenous Artist (2022-2024), and the 2025 SaskMusic Award for Contemporary Indigenous Artist.  She gained national recognition for her performance of the Canadian anthem in Cree, English, and French at the 109th Grey Cup.  Her voice and achievements have established her as a standout artist in the Canadian country music scene.";
