iwts_performer:9244 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Paige Rutledge";
  schema:description "Paige Rutledge sparkles on stage-both figuratively, and literally. Her vibrant personality and rhinestone-studded guitar elevate her already commanding presence. Paige released her debut EP, “Break Up Rules”, in September 2024. “Break Up Rules” has been featured as the Fresh Pick across Bayshore Broadcasting stations (January 2025) as well as Sirius XM's Top of the Country. \"Break Up Rules\" EP has over 600,000 global streams. The single \"Dive Bar Romeo\" was released in February of 2025 and in it's first 2 weeks has over 50,000 streams.";
  schema:url <https://www.paigerutledge.com>;
