  schema:name "TAP INTO SOUL: America’s Premier Tap-Dancing Soul Singer";
  schema:description "Blending multi-octave vocals and world-class tap dancing in a soulful setlist featuring both classic and contemporary chart-topping hits, Solomon Jaye’s TAP INTO SOUL offers an exciting new take on a timeless genre of music. From James Brown to Bruno Mars, the music featured in this show transports listeners from the 1950s to today in the blink of an eye! If you haven’t experienced the incredible cross-genre mashup of music, dance, and electrifying energy created every time Solomon Jaye steps onto the stage, it’s time to TAP INTO SOUL!";
