  schema:description "The Dust Rhinos are a high-energy Celtic folk rock band from Winnipeg, Canada, with a unique sound that blends traditional Celtic music with modern rock and roll. With their dynamic performances and infectious energy, the Dust Rhinos are sure to get your feet tapping and your body moving. Whether you're a fan of Celtic music, rock, or just great live performances, the Dust Rhinos are the perfect choice for your next event. So come along for the ride and let the Dust Rhinos take you on a wild musical journey you won't soon forget!";
