iwts_performer:9327 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "2Moods";
  schema:description """2Moods is a French-speaking artist from Congo Kinshasa. His
love for music and his admiration for French vocabulary are the source of motivation for his pursuit of a musical career. A fan of the Hip Hop/Rap and Afro sound genres, the artist has been active on the Canadian music scene since summer 2015. Each year, the lyricist makes several appearances on stage across the country, during events bringing together music lovers from different age groups.
2Mood’s ultimate goal is to educate and entertain through his
music.""";
