  schema:description "Katie-Ellen Humphries is a comedian, writer and theatre creator best known for their work on CBC Radio’s The Debaters. A founding member of the sketch group The Lady Show (“Pick Of the Fringe” Vancouver 2019), and former writer/performer with award-winning theatre cabaret company Atomic Vaudeville, Katie-Ellen’s venture into solo theatre earned sold-out runs and hold-over performances at the 2023 Victoria and Vancouver Fringe Festivals and a “Top 15 Shows to Watch” distinction at the 2024 San Diego Fringe.";
