  schema:name "Orchid Orchestra";
  schema:description "Orchid Orchestra is a Vancouver-based indie pop band creating lush choral harmonies, shimmering synths, and cinematic electronic textures that balance emotional depth with kinetic energy. Fronted by therapist and songwriter Rupert Hudson, the band blends heartfelt songwriting with themes of vulnerability, self-acceptance, and connection. They are currently recording their first full-length album.";
