  schema:name "Kim Thompson";
  schema:description "Singer, songwriter, “Sippin on Love” hit #4  “Dear Dolly\", hit #8.  2023“Just Anybody\", hit #1  , “Hey Cowboy” charted #2 .  “Heartache Heartbreak” hit #2 on charts, Picked up by Sirius Radio and “Game Of Love”.  Nominated for awards in ISSA USA and Europe’s Fairplay Awards for Female Artist, credits in Disney, Heartland, Fargo .   CCMA Awards.  CMAB, YCC Awards. SOCAN Travel Grant, and award winner 2024  ISSA. Anthem singing Canadian Pro Rodeo and on the ice at the BCJHL. Co-host Black Dog Indie Radio Georgia and Denver USA.";
