iwts_performer:9401 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Aileé Zaga";
  schema:description """Aileé Zaga is an art pop songwriter-producer based in British Columbia. Influenced by boundary-pushing acts like Björk and Imogen Heap, she artfully incorporates elements of electronic, classical, and alternative music, creating a balance between memorable melodies and experimental sounds. 

Zaga’s 2023 single, Written in the Earth, received praise from The Permanent Rain Press and Canadian Beats. She has been featured in outlets like Global Okanagan and KelownaNow and received a “Best of Kelowna 2024” nomination for “Best Local Musician”.""";
