  schema:name "ALPHA CENTAURI";
  schema:description "ALPHA CENTAURI is a mix genre artist (hip hop/r&b/funk/soul/pop) based in Vancouver/Nanaimo who generally plays with a full 7-piece live band. His music boast strong melodies and conscious lyrics - often with uplifting themes about motivation and class struggle.  ALPHA CENTAURI has performed and toured with a number of multi-platinum/Grammy nominated hip hop artists including Ja Rule, Method Man./Redman, Chali 2na/Cut Chemist (of Jurassic 5) and has an upcoming tours )cross Canada) with Macklemore; Europe tour with Method Man/ Redman. More TBA.";
