iwts_performer:9422 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Rachella Wred";
  schema:description "Singer-songwriter Rachella Wred is a West Coast transplant currently living in Montreal. Split between the ambience of the Montreal bustle and the pull of the Pacific Ocean and equipped with her acoustic guitar, SP404, synth, and intimate songwriting, she has filled rooms across Canada. She has been featured in Exclaim, CBC, The Line of Best Fit, Billboard Canada, Range Magazine, and Montreal Guardian. Written around intimate endings and beginnings, Leave The Light On, is Rachella Wred’s debut album.";
