  schema:name "Los Duendes";
  schema:description "Los Duendes brings the spirit of global psychedelia to the heart of Vancouver's music scene, weaving together Cumbia, Afro-Cuban rhythms, and roots music into an electrifying tapestry of sound. This five-piece ensemble, whose name evokes the mischievous and magical spirits of Latin American folklore, transforms every venue into an unstoppable dance party with their unique fusion of traditional and contemporary styles.";
