iwts_performer:9439 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Matt Falk";
  schema:description """Matt Falk is a comedian, writer & actor who the CBC called, “Effortlessly Funny.”
You’ve heard him on Sirius Satellite Radio, Laugh Out Loud & The Debaters. His Dry Bar Comedy specials have millions of views collectively online & 3 of his comedy albums reached #1 on the iTunes Comedy charts.
You’ve seen him at The Ha!lifax Comedy Festival, The Winnipeg Comedy Festival & Just For Laughs in Montreal.
He was named one of the “BEST OF THE FEST” at the Burbank Comedy Festival in California & he placed 2nd in The World Series of Comedy in Las Vegas.""";
