  schema:name "ES:MO (Elizabeth Shepherd & Michael Occhipinti)";
  schema:description "ES:MO is Elizabeth Shepherd and Michael Occhipinti, two celebrated musicians with a combined 17 JUNO nominations, including their debut The Weight of Hope. Long admired as individuals, ES:MO pairs Elizabeth Shepherd’s soulful voice with Michael Occhipinti’s virtuosic palette of guitar sounds. Initially built on interpretations of great singer-songwriters, their upcoming release SUNSHINE IN MY BONES showcases their original compositions, using found sounds, electronic loops, and the vision of two of Canada’s most respected musicians.";
