iwts_performer:9451 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Van Lefan";
  schema:description "Van Lefan (??) is a Taiwanese interdisciplinary artist working with sound, movement, theatre, and visual arts. As a singer songwriter she uses her voice, guitar, flute, and electronics, to moves between folk, pop, and experimental sound, sharing songs that are reflections of personal and collective experiences. Her works serve as spaces to process, explore potential, change, and co-create a world of our imaginations.";
