iwts_performer:9467 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Duo Aster";
  schema:description """The Duo Aster embodies the union of two dynamic and talented musicians: Clio Theodoridis, saxophonist, and Jonathan Nemtanu, pianist.

The duo now performs across Canada, France, Greece, and China at various concerts and festivals, such as the Aegean International Arts Festival, the Festival Intime de Musique des Bergeronnes, the Rendez-vous Musicaux de Laterrière, the Jiangsu Grand Theater in Nanjing and the 2024 Shanghai International Arts Festival.

Today, the duo strives to enhance the reputation of classical saxophone in Canada and beyond.""";
