iwts_performer:9484 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Adam Cousins";
  schema:description "Adam Cousins is turning heads as a traditional country singer/songwriter from Central Ontario. In 2022, Cousins took home 2 FCLMA for Country Artist of the Year and Music Video of the Year. Since then Adam has released a catalogue of songs, including Top 30 single \"Our Lives\" and 2024 summer anthem \"Ain't We Having Fun Yet\". Adam has performed aside Aaron Pritchett, Jess Moskaluke, Brett Kissel, and many more. With brand new music recorded in Nashville and a summer schedule full of live shows, Cousins is gearing up for an exciting 2025 season!";
