iwts_performer:9485 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Floydian Waters";
  schema:description """With a massive lineup of 14 exceptionally talented musicians & technicians, they pay homage to the legendary sounds of Pink Floyd. They dive deep into the catalog of Pink Floyd, captivating audiences with their faithful renditions of the band’s greatest hits, as well as some obscure gold!

From the psychedelic landscapes of “Astromony Domine” to the progressive epics of “Sheep” and beyond, their repertoire spans Pink Floyd’s entire discography, including a mesmerizing rendition of the entire ground breaking album, “Dark Side of The Moon”.""";
