  schema:name "Les Productions du 10 avril";
  schema:description "Founded in 2020 to connect musical and theatrical genres, Les Productions du 10 avril produces versatile performances for diverse audiences. Jazz concerts and lyrical shows blend rather than separate styles, fostering closer connections between artists and the public. This shared experience fuels artistic evolution, allowing art to grow within our ever-changing society.";
