  schema:name "Luka Kawabata";
  schema:description "Luka Kawabata is a multilingual opera singer, producer, and content creator based in Vancouver, Canada. Passionate about culture, language, and personal development, Luka explores identity and storytelling through The HAFU Project, which highlights the experiences of mixed-Japanese individuals. Born in Japan, Luka's artistic practice largely explores the intersections of language, cultural connection, and personal growth while inspiring others to embrace their unique identities.";
