  schema:name "Jelly B & The Kmart Shoppers";
  schema:description "Jelly B & The Kmart Shoppers are an acoustic trio who share a love of playing music and having fun. Their blend of roots, blues and folk rock tunes always has the audience clapping and singing along. Add in original songs and players who will trade off on a wide mix of instruments and you’ve got everything you need for your entertainment shopping list.  Celebrating 15 years together and still having way too much fun.";
