iwts_performer:9516 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "J. Leon Pridgen II";
  schema:description """Leon is an actor, writer, playwright and producer.  He can be seen in television shows ranging from HBO's The Righteous Gemstones starring John Goodman, to the Starz series Hightown starring Monica Raymund and James Bade Dale.  Film credits include Careful What You Wish For starring Nick Jonas and Dermot Mulroney to Heaven Sent opposite Karen Abercrombie.  

Leon is also a veteran of the US Army whose time is service was spent with the 82nd Airborne Division at Fort Bragg, NC.

Leon's motto is Dream Big - You May Never Wake Up!!""";
