iwts_performer:9534 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Nick Demopoulos";
  schema:description "S.M.O.M.I.D (string Modeling midi device) is a project by Nick Demopoulos, a musician, instrument builder and international touring artist. Smomid utilizes instruments he has designed to create audiovisual performances.  These instruments create sound, emit light and control video animations. He has toured throughout the U.S. and Internationally, with appearances at Lincoln Center in New York, the Montreux jazz festival, several tours in South East Asia and the Middle East and has worked as a Cultural Diplomat for the U.S. State Department.";
