iwts_performer:9554 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Harmonica Pocket";
  schema:description """The Harmonica Pocket is all about creating empowering musical experiences for youth & families with kids.

Silly and sweet the band performs up and down the East & West Coasts at theaters, clubs, festivals, parks, libraries and schools.

Audiences are drawn in by catchy songs and unexpected props. Humor, improv & play are generously sprinkled on top.

Currently touring as an acoustic looping artist, frontman Keeth Apgar plays instruments one at a time to create layers of sounds – ukulele, bass, wah-wah guitar, harmonica, percussion & vocals.""";
