iwts_performer:9557 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Cassidy Dickens";
  schema:description """Marrying a powerful sense of traditional Appalachian storytelling with a modern folk sound, West Virginian artist Cassidy Dickens brings a “unique fusion of vulnerability, resilience, unguarded sincerity, and soul-stirring melodies” to the world of acoustic Americana. (HONK MAGAZINE)
With more than 15 years of touring, 7 years of professional songwriting, three full-length albums, and several songwriting awards under her belt—  her newest album, All I’m Missing was met with critical acclaim and an appearance on the 'Tunesday' Show with WDTV.""";
