  schema:name "Bridgette Yarwood";
  schema:description "Bridgette Yarwood is a multi-genre singer/songwriter from Lethbridge, Alberta, with over 20 years of stage experience. Her music is described as piano rock, blending elements of jazz, pop, and R&B. Known for her powerful, commanding voice, Bridgette’s sound is emotionally charged, backed by an amazing and tight band that lend bold guitar riffs and a strong rhythm section. Her raw, unapologetic style and magnetic stage presence leave a lasting impact.";
