iwts_performer:9570 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Skystar";
  schema:description """Now, with his first JUNO Award nomination for best Reggae Recording  at the 2025 JUNO Awards, Skystar isn’t on his way—he’s already here.
If reggae and dancehall have a pulse in Western Canada, Skystar is the heartbeat. A powerhouse in Canada’s reggae scene, he’s built a name with his high-energy sound and undeniable stage presence globally. His latest EP (Sky’s The Limit) is making waves, stacking over 200,000 streams on Spotify. Tracks like Karma and Learnt are spinning on CBC Radio’s Key of A and Rebelvibez’ s Top 10 Canadian Reggae Chart.""";
