  schema:name "Marie Flipo-Bergeron";
  schema:description """Singer-songwriter Marie brings a soulful voice with tasteful folk & bluesy sound to your event. Performing mainly as a solo artist, Marie and her acoustic guitar will transport you through original songs, and her renditions of old and newer classics. 

