  schema:name "Molly in the Mineshaft";
  schema:description "“Newgrass” group Molly in the Mineshaft seeks a balance of celebrating the musical heritage of bluegrass music and presenting it with a new twist. Their purpose is to uplift, entertain, and inspire people of all ages through high-energy, diverse music. They’ll wow the audience with their upbeat take on traditional favorites from around the world, mixed with roots-inspired original compositions.";
