  schema:name "The Crickettes";
  schema:description "The Crickettes are a Calgary-based folk duo crafting harmony-rich, story-driven songs that balance intimacy with polish. Their sound blends classic folk warmth with modern sensibility, brought to life through dynamic live performances and standout musicianship. With growing radio play, festival appearances across Alberta, and sold-out hometown shows, they are quickly gaining momentum. Whether on a main stage or in an intimate room, The Crickettes deliver songs that connect, linger, and resonate.";
