iwts_performer:9637 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Jenner Fox Band";
  schema:description """\"Sometimes, we forget to notice the way the light hits the floor, or how the wind shifts just before rain. And sometimes, all it takes is a quiet sound, a familiar voice, a single line of melody, to pull us gently back into the moment – to remind us we’re still here. Such is the power of \"Anything\" the new  Jenner Fox Band LP.\" - Atwood Magazine

Since their conception on a cargo bicycle tour in 2021, the Bellingham based Jenner Fox Band has delighted audiences up and down the west coast. The five piece band also doubles as Paul Simon Tribute.""";
  schema:url <https://jennerfox.com/>;
