  schema:name "The Dreamboats";
  schema:description "The Dreamboats are a high-energy quartet reviving the spirit of 1950s and ’60s rock ’n’ roll with charisma, tight musicianship, and vintage style. Blending the sounds of Elvis Presley, Buddy Holly, and The Beatles with fresh energy, they deliver an electrifying, all-live show—slick guitar work, rich harmonies, and an immersive experience that gets audiences dancing, singing, and reliving their youth. Touring extensively across North America and Europe, with highlights including Liverpool’s iconic The Cavern Club and Graceland.”";
