  schema:description "Nashville’s Six One Five Collective is a collaborative of Nationally awarded artists and songwriters with 3 Grammy nominations & an IBMA Song of the Year honor. Their songs have been recorded by George Strait, Lee Brice, Marc Broussard, Sister Hazel, and TV shows Nashville, Parenthood, and Virgin River! Nicole Witt, Sarah Darling, Aaron Goodvin & Michael Logen’s distinctive harmonies are likened to Little Big Town & Fleetwood Mac. They’ve toured extensively in North America and overseas and their show blends their originals with iconic covers";
