  schema:name "Rosewood Ave";
  schema:description "Multiple CMAOntario nominated duo of the year and CBC Searchlight Outstanding Country artist winner Rosewood Ave is a hot new act mixing traditional and contemporary sounds. Their recent singles have seen major features such as Top 100 Canadian Country Radio Charts, Sirius XM Top of the Country Emerging Artist, and Spotify's editorial country playlists. Rosewood Ave is no stranger to the stage, having opened up for major acts such as Lainey Wilson, Red Clay Strays, Dallas Smith, Dean Brody, The Reklaws and James Barker Band.";
