  schema:name "Tanu";
  schema:description "Born and raised in India, Tanu Sharma is a dance artist and a choreographer. She received her MA from India and MS from NCSU, USA. Over the years she has performed at various venues including Stewart Theatre, Carolina Theatre of Durham, Nasher Museum, Durham Arts council, Cary Arts Center etc. She has participated in several cultural outreach programs, lecture demonstrations and served as a judge for local and international dance competitions. She believes in a lifelong pursuit of learning while exploring creativity and pushing boundaries.";
