  schema:name "Mbira Renaissance Band";
  schema:description """Fusing the traditional Zimbabwean mbira instrument with contemporary guitar, keyboard and brass instruments, the Mbira Renaissance Band offers a fresh, energetic yet delicately balanced sonic experience. Cyclical and simultaneously improvisational, the Mbira Renaissance Band serves a unique take on the contemporary mbira sound with splashes of reggae, afro jazz, chimurenga and afro-pop.

Twice nominated for the Edmonton Music Awards, the band is currently working on its third studio album, with a release planned for spring/summer 2025""";
