  schema:description """Ladies of the 80’s! A musical tribute and more dedicated to the legendary & iconic female vocalists of the 1980’s! Located in central North Carolina, Vivian Elliott our youthful and energetic vocalist and musical tour guide, will lead you through the Music and Sounds of the Incredible 1980’s era, complete with Awesome 80’s Songs, Colorful 80’s Visuals, Showmanship, and the FUN of the 80’s!

