iwts_performer:9720 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "The Lubben Brothers";
  schema:description """The Lubben Brothers are a nationally touring Americana/folk duo blending heartland storytelling with soaring harmonies and high-energy acoustic drive. Fans of Mumford & Sons, The Lumineers, and The Avett Brothers will immediately connect — but what makes the Lubbens stand out is their authenticity and brotherly chemistry that feels tailor-made.

Instant Audience Connection
Their ability to create a shared emotional experience translates powerfully in a showcase setting.

Presenters are not just entertained — they see clear programming value.""";
