iwts_performer:9723 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Ryland Moranz";
  schema:description "Ryland Moranz has come into his own in these strange times. A folk/bluegrass multi instrumentalist and singer-songwriter from Lethbridge, Alberta in the traditional territory of the  Siksika, Piikani and Kainai peoples, Ryland has stepped into the great beyond, empathetically  exploring his own stories and the stories of others. His compositions span bygone days, the here and now, and what may yet be to come, both for himself and for us all. With a voice tempered by both joy and sorrow, Moranz channels the spirit of a songwriter’s songwriter.";
  schema:url <https://www.rylandmoranz.com/>;
