  schema:name "Legend of the Pioneers";
  schema:description "The Legends of the Pioneers' is packed with stories and songs from entertainers in several genres of music and film.  From the Silver Screen Cowboys to  Western Swing greats  and, Classic Country stars.  They pay tribute to Pop greats  and, once in a while, some good ol' Rock and Roll. Recognizable songs that make the audience sing along. The life and times of the legendary entertainment icons - all told in story and song with incredible three-part harmony and wrapped in rhinestones.";
