iwts_performer:9738 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Matt Beatty";
  schema:description """Matt Beatty is an award winning singer/songwriter. Over the last 20 years Matt has performed across Canada and around the world. 
“Songs From My Dads Old Guitar” was released in mid 2025. The album features 10 original songs such as “Never Enough Time” & “Lovesick Fools” alongside a few reclaimed classics.
Matt has released 3 Christmas songs.  His group, DoubleSuede, released \"the deEP End\" in 2023. 
Matt was featured performing in the premier episode of Paramount's “Joe Pickett” and is a winner on CTV’s Battle Of The Generations game show.""";
