iwts_performer:9739 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "DoubleSuede";
  schema:description """DoubleSuede is a modern blending of classic 50’s & 60’s Rock & Country. Featuring a hard to describe sound because you can’t believe it’s only two musicians performing. Casey on the upright bass with Matt on guitars & vocals. 
\"Black Widow\"& \"Dive Bar Debutante\"  were singles released from \"The deEP End\" album which got the group nominated as duo of the year at the YYC Music Awards 2023
Expect a new 13 song album coming out later in 2025.  The live off the floor recording will feature crowd favourites plus new original material.""";
