  schema:name "Sydney Riley";
  schema:description "Sydney Riley is an ISSA and Josie-nominated Singer/Songwriter from Wasaga Beach, Ontario. Influences include the likes of Led Zeppelin, Florence & The Machine, and Joan Jett. Sydney blends colourful imagery stemming from folk music with hard rock riffs and beats, their powerful voice being the cherry on top. Sydney is reinventing what it means to be a performer.";
