  schema:name "The Upsy Daisies";
  schema:description "The Upsy Daisies are a children’s music duo from Atlantic Canada creating joyful, interactive songs and performances that celebrate confidence, individuality, and inclusion. With playful harmonies, catchy originals, and reimagined classics, they inspire kids and families to sing, dance, and dream together. Their shows combine music, storytelling, and audience participation, making every performance a fun and memorable experience for young audiences and the young at heart.";
