iwts_performer:9780 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "CJ";
  schema:description "Known as ‘a mixed bag of tricks', CJ is an innovative, Moncton-based musical theatre/drag performer.  He is the creator and star of the acclaimed drag musical comedies \"Jingle Belle\" and \"Flyin Solo!\" You may have also seen CJ on the Capitol Theatre stage as Scuttle in The Little Mermaid or Pugsley in The Addams Family. CJ is a two-time recipient of Moncton's 'Platinum Entertainer' award. Fans say CJ has “amazing energy that lights up a room” and is “able to connect with the crowd and make you feel like you are a part of the show.”";
