  schema:name "Tyler Hache";
  schema:description "Tyler Hache is an award-winning singer-songwriter from Moncton, New Brunswick. His debut album Silent earned Music NB’s Solo Recording of the Year and opened doors to performances alongside distinguished acts like Leif Vollebekk and David Myles, as well as regular co-writing trips on Nashville’s Music Row. With songs featured in film and television, Hache’s October 2025 single “Meredith” marks the beginning of a new chapter.";
