iwts_performer:9845 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Theo Day";
  schema:description "Theo Day is a rising Canadian folk-pop artist known for heartfelt storytelling and acoustic-led production. His debut single (August 13, 2025) gained rapid traction, surpassing 70,000 global streams as listeners connected with his honest lyricism and nostalgic tone. Often compared to Noah Kahan and Cameron Whitcomb, Theo’s growing online presence earned Billboard recognition on November 25, 2025. He is now developing his sophomore EP and expanding his reach across Canada.";
