  schema:name "Stundom";
  schema:description "Inspired by the traditional dance music of their ancestors, the music of Stundom invites you into a wondrous immersive world, and mixes folk traditions with classical chamber music and modern symphonic elements. With a blend of the violin, the cittern and the piano, Emma Kragh-Elmoe, Villads Hoffmann and Julian Svejgaard share a unique musical chemistry and ability to create capturing melodies.";
