  schema:name "The Spontaneous Shakespeare Company";
  schema:description "The Spontaneous Shakespeare Company is Canada's premiere improvised Shakespeare performance troupe. Established in 2016 as Shakespeare After Dark, they have performed their award winning sell-out shows all around the country. Their formats include the tragedy \"Breaking Bard\", the romantic comedy \"Much Ado About Blank\" and their history format \"Whose Lineage is it Anyway?\"";
