  schema:name "Northern Air";
  schema:description """Northern Air is rooted in the belief that music carries stories across time, culture, and geography. Our songs draw from the vast skies, rivers, and plains of the prairies, while weaving in themes of resilience, belonging, and community. 

We see our artistic practice as a bridge between traditions and audiences. Northern Air honours the folk tradition of storytelling while embracing contemporary approaches to songwriting and performance.""";
