iwts_performer:9881 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Joe Callahan";
  schema:description """Joe Callahan is a folk/roots/blues singer-songwriter who first performed professionally over 40 years ago  in a country-rock band called The Rivermen.

 In 2011, Joe co-produced his first CD \"Watching the Light\".  In 2019 Joe recorded and released an EP, \"Street Level High\" accompanied by multi-instrumentalist Peter Snell and bassist Mike Acerra. Joe recorded his 3rd CD of original music \"Mystery\", a live recording with bassist Howard Baer in 2020. 
Joe met guitarist Tim Campbell from Rosthern SK  and they perform regularly around Saskatoon.""";
