iwts_performer:9883 a schema:Organization;
  schema:name "Yvonne Montoya/Safos Dance Theatre";
  schema:description """Safos Dance Theatre's mission is to create contemporary artistic forms that reflect the common experiences of our diverse community. Focusing on Latina and Southwest dance artists, Safos focuses on encouraging innovative movements and embracing the use of aesthetics and art forms unique to the Southwest to represent the cultural diversity of the US/Mexico borderlands. 

 Yvonne Montoya (Artistic Director) is a mother, choreographer, writer. Montoya was the first Arizonan to receive the National Dance Project Production Grant.""";
