  schema:name "New Ohio";
  schema:description "New Ohio is the name under which Broadway veterans Matt Cusack and Allison Kelly Perform. The name comes from the marriage of their musical upbringings, Matt grew up in New Jersey studying Jazz and Allison was raised in Ohio steeped in traditional country music. Together they share a passion for Western swing and Country music and their show \"Because You're Mine: Johnny, June and the Greatest Country Duets of All Time\" is reflective of that.";
