  schema:description "Luke Vandergriff is a musician, storyteller, and instrument-builder who creates original music from recycled and everyday objects. His family-friendly and educational performances blend rhythm, imagination, and narrative, inviting audiences to see creativity in unexpected places. Drawing inspiration from his work with children in Latin America, Luke’s shows celebrate creativity, teach emotional resilience, raise environmental awareness, inspire cultural appreciation and uplift the audience.";
