  schema:description "Jill Loryn is a singer-songwriter and folk artist from small-town Ontario, known for her quiet intensity and sharp storytelling. Her writing pulls from real life - relationships, expectations, and the tension of growing up somewhere everyone knows your name. With a grounded, unpolished honesty reminiscent of early Kathleen Edwards, Jill’s songs are intimate, observant, and built to last.";
  schema:url <https://www.instagram.com/jilllorynmusic>;
