iwts_performer:9927 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Jay Davis";
  schema:description """The band is comprised of musicians who have played with artists like Chloe Watkinson, Rhonda Stakich, Holly Cole, Donne Roberts, Rich Underhill, Sarah Slean, Fred Penner and Ken Whitely.

Ontario's own Jay Davis has worked as a guest vocalist for the Hamilton Philharmonic Orchestra. Disney Cruise Lines, Holland America, Princess Cruise Lines, ,and The Niagara Symphony Orchestra. He has a varied and extensive resume in England’s famous West End, Germany, and Canada with over 100 professional credits on stage and screen.""";
