  schema:name "Tabitha Meeks";
  schema:description """The Queen of Retro Pop has arrived! 
Best described as “Norah Jones meets Nancy Sinatra”, Tabitha Meeks’ feel good throwback music will make you bop your head, tap your toes and feel empowered all at once.

Her piano solos and live shows are unmatched in fun vintage energy, and her catchy light-hearted songs will be stuck in your head for days.""";
