iwts_performer:9943 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Joan Bessie Duo";
  schema:description """The self-titled debut “Joan Bessie” (2018) had several playing in regular rotation on CBC Music, including the  lead single “G.G.”,  which spent 10 weeks on the CBC Music Top 20 chart, hitting #3.

In 2023, The Joan Bessie Duo was formed and began touring to support the release of the sophomore album “Girls I’ve Lost”, featuring her daughter Sophie on vocals and bass. Both the album and live show have been met with critical acclaim.

The latest Joan Bessie single, \"Dark Voices\" (2025) hit #29 on Canadian Indie Country Chart.""";
