  schema:name "Daisy Blue Groff";
  schema:description """Daisy Blue Groff is a Canadian songsmith, vocalist, and guitar slinger carving out a space in a genre of her own making: Metaphysical Avant-Garde Canadiana.
Her latest sonic exploration, SHIFTSHAPER, is set to be released in August of 2026. A seasoned performer, Daisy Blue Groff has toured across Canada, the United States, and Europe, including Iceland, Holland, Germany, and Belgium. Her trajectory was defined by the success of her band, Painting Daisies, who rose above all acts to win CBC’s Great Canadian Music Dream Polaris Prize""";
