  schema:name "Eloise Coopersmith";
  schema:description "loise Coopersmith is a theatre artist, writer, and producer creating engaging, tour-ready work that blends humor, music, and storytelling. Her performances center on themes of heartfelt, feel-good love and human connection, offering accessible, uplifting experiences that resonate across diverse communities. Through her touring productions, she partners with presenters to deliver programs that not only entertain, but foster meaningful audience engagement and connection.";
