  schema:description "Performing as CC Duo, classical guitarists Adam Cicchillitti and Steve Cowan are redefining the guitar duo with refined artistry and bold, contemporary programming. Winners of second and third prize at the GFA International Ensemble Competition (2023, 2021), they’ve earned acclaim for their albums Focus (ECMA Classical Recording of the Year) and Intimate Impressions, and pursue with a new release, Lyrique, (September 2025) on Analekta.";
