iwts_performer:10017 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Chloé Dumoulin";
  schema:description "Named one of CBC Music’s “30 Under 30,” pianist Chloé Dumoulin is emerging as a leading artist of her generation. Praised for her expressive sensitivity and command of sonority, she performs internationally, including at Carnegie Hall. She has appeared as soloist with the Orchestre Métropolitain and Orchestre symphonique de Laval, and debuted with the Orchestre symphonique de Drummondville in 2026. A 2025 Guildhall graduate, her debut album Nouveau lyrisme was released by Leaf Music.";
