  schema:description "Paul Tedeschini is an award winning sound editor, sound designer, mixing and mastering engineer, musician, actor and voice performer.Select theatre credits include If You Could Read My MInd - The Songs Of Gordon Lightfoot, I Think I'm Fallin' - The Songs Of Joni Mitchell, Home Is A Beautiful Word, Puttin’ On The Ritz, Mom’s The Word, Vanya, Sonya, Masha and Spike ( The Belfry Theatre). Sweeny Todd, Red Hot Cole, Gaslight ( Bluebridge Theatre ). Into The Woods, Cabaret (Canadian College For The Performing Arts).";
