  schema:description "Motus creates original plays for young audiences and their families. The company works in puppetry arts and live music, building bridges and fostering free-flowing dialogue between cultures. With its resolutely global outlook, the company embraces and emphasizes collaboration with artists from everywhere, through national and international co-productions.";
