iwts_performer:10094 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Carson Rhodes";
  schema:description "Join us on a musical journey hosted by Carson Rhodes as he shares his insights and experiences on how some of these great compositions came into existence and recount direct conversations he had with Billy and his original band members. Carson and his band will be performing songs from Billy Joel’s favorite artists like Ray Charles, The Beatles, Jimi Hendrix and then perform the Billy Joel hits that these songs were influenced by! It’s sure to be a great night of music for the whole family!";
