  schema:name "In Spite Of Ourselves";
  schema:description """In Spite of Ourselves is a night celebrating the musical legacy of John Prine. The band features: Tom Landa of The Paperboys/Locarno, Kalissa Landa also of The Paperboys, Steve Mitchell of Travels With Charley, and seasoned veteran /producer/ Doug Cox. 

This is NOT a tribute act but rather a celebration of John’s music done in a round robin  style by celebrated BC songwriters and musicians.""";
