iwts_performer:10119 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Marc Beaudin";
  schema:description """Marc Beaudin is a veteran of the Alberta music scene. 2025 Juno award nominee with Samantha King and The Midnight Outfit, and winner of two Global Music Awards for Composition and Production for his album \"Jazz Cafe de Cuba\".  Marc is virtuosic abilities on Spanish guitar are weekly featured at Atrium at Sabor in Edmonton, presenting is VINO and GUITAR LATINO show.

Marc presents his brand new ''all francophone\" album : Prairies Funko-Fone is a heartfelt tribute to Western Canada. This wonderful album was recorded at Louis Sedmak's Studio.""";
