  schema:description "Iam a singer song writer. Played in bands, looking to form a solid band. I play Guitar and sing (drums also). I have performed on alot of well known stages such as the Burton Cummins Theater, The RBC convention center, The Red River Exhibition, the 2026 Voices of the North showcase found on YouTube. I have many friends already in the industry. Such as the C-weed Band, Nelson Little, Billy Joe Greene, Desiree Dorian, and many more that have inspired me to become just as they are. Grate talented ppl.";
