iwts_performer:10123 a schema:Organization;
  schema:name "Bare Bait Dance";
  schema:description """Founded in 2011 by Joy French, Bare Bait Dance is a 501c3, professional dance company based in Missoula, MT.

Over the past 15 years, BBD has grown to include a full-season paid professional company, artist residencies, weekly classes/workshops, an annual film festival, and more.

We are so honored that audiences and dancers alike continue to be curious about what contemporary dance and performance is and can be.

Find Bare Bait Dance at its home venue: Missoula's Westside Theater.""";
