iwts_performer:10126 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Duo Balalaika";
  schema:description "Duo Balalaika's music merges multiple cultures through a rare combination of instruments – balalaika, piano, and voice, across continents, across time, and composers. Audiences are introduced to classic compositions, virtuoso variations, toe-tapping get up and dance music. Repertoire includes original arrangements that mingle music from different worlds where you can experience innovative, musical relationships. Think film scores to tango, bluegrass to gypsy music, ragtime to romances.";
