iwts_performer:10129 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Allen Christie & The Hot Brands";
  schema:description "Straight from Alberta, Allen Christie delivers pure, unfiltered acoustic roots music with a hearty dose of western charm. For over 26 years, Allen has been living and breathing music, carving out a name as a top-notch entertainer, studio musician, and producer. He’s recorded six original albums(his latest, Big Dreams, dropped in 2024) and has worked with countless other artists, shaping songs that stay true to the prairie spirit. With a new group of musicians called \"The Hot Brands\" Allen has been exciting stages all across Alberta and beyond.";
