iwts_performer:10145 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "NexDetour";
  schema:description "Are there really only 3 people singing? YES! At times, you may even think you hear guitars and drums, but it is the versatile voices of Dayton based a cappella power trio, NexDetour. Jim, Ryan, and Scott have shared the stage with The Beach Boys and The Temptations. Their repertoire is a rock, pop, soul, and doo-wop tour though time that appeals to all ages. They have over 25 years experience weaving harmonies together and building fun, interactive, fully choreographed stage shows. Don’t miss NexDetour live! You won’t believe your ears.";
