iwts_performer:10148 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Angela Combs";
  schema:description "MY NAME IS ANGELA COMBS. I WAS BORN IN MISSISSIPPI. I THINK THAT IS RELEVANT BECAUSE THAT IS HOW SOUTHERN GOSPEL, COUNTRY AND DELTA BLUES WERE ADDED TO MY SOUNDTRACK. I HAVE LOVED MUSIC MY ENTIRE LIFE. I AM SMART BUT ECLECTIC, GOOFY, SOCIALLY AWKWARD ESPECIALLY IN NEW SITUATIONS, NON-CONFRONTATIONAL, WEIRDLY SHY FOR A SINGER AND GENERALLY KIND. I JUST WANT OUR LITTLE BAND TO PLAY MUSIC WE LOVE FOR PEOPLE WHO LOVE MUSIC. IF YOU LIKE HIPPY SOUL, COUNTRY, FUNK, ROOTS, BLUES, AMERICANA MUSIC THEN YOU SHOULD COME SEE OUR BAND! LOVE YA’LL!";
