  schema:name "176 Keys Dueling Pianos";
  schema:description """A 176 Keys Dueling Piano show isn’t just a performance—it’s an experience. We deliver a high-energy dueling piano show that turns any event into a party. Interactive and audience-driven, our shows engage all ages with live music, humour, and crowd participation.

