iwts_performer:10153 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Allison Road";
  schema:description "Allison Road is female-fronted band (or duo) that plays all of your favorite Country hits, and sprinkles Rock, Classic Rock and Pop into  the mix to keep a good variety of genres! Their original music, while maintaining a country feel, toes the line of all 3 genres and is written from the real life experiences of frontwoman, Alli Sarven.  They put the work in to ensure a flawless and professional performance, while showcasing their talent, the love of the stage and their sincere love of music and community!";
