  schema:name "Hayley Isabel";
  schema:description "Hayley Isabel is a singer-songwriter from Airdrie, Alberta, with energy beyond her years. At 14, she’s a 3x Alberta Country Music Horizon Youth Artist of the Year (2024, 2025, 2026). Her music blends heartfelt storytelling with the spirit of 90s rock, inspired by artists like Ella Langley and Cameron Whitcomb. Hayley is a hair-flippin’ firecracker with bold talent, big dreams, and a fierce drive to make them reality.";
