iwts_performer:10165 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "The Barrel Boys";
  schema:description """A bluegrass powerhouse featuring rich vocal harmonies, killer picking, and a fun-loving, down-to-earth stage presence, The Barrel Boys are a unique staple of Canadian roots music. Informed by the traditions of bluegrass, country, and old-time, The Boys have crafted their unmistakable sound into a joyful and deeply soulful musical experience.
The Barrel Boys' fourth album “Chicken in the Window” has earned them nominations for “Vocal Group of the Year” and “Traditional Album of the Year” at the upcoming 2026 Canadian Folk Music Awards.""";
