  schema:name "Jonathan Blanchard's From History to Hip-Hop";
  schema:description "Experience the power of arts integration with From History to Hip-Hop, the signature program of Lincoln Center Certified teaching artist, spirituals preservationist, and operatic vocalist Jonathan Blanchard and his band. This high-energy, interactive performance takes audiences on a musical journey spanning 250 years of American music—connecting field songs and spirituals to all of today’s modern genres, blues, jazz, country, soul, funk, rock, and hip hop—captivating students and bringing communities together through a shared concert experience";
