  schema:name "RAGS AND RICHES";
  schema:description "RAGS AND RICHES is the alt-pop duo of brothers Tanner and Peyton Whitt. With over 14 million streams, multiple awards, and 350+ shows across 45 states, they’ve built a fast-rising national presence while supporting acts like Smash Mouth, Fitz & the Tantrums, and Judah & the Lion. Their releases, including Always Gold and I NEED A HOLIDAY, showcase their infectious sound and growing impact.";
