iwts_performer:10197 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Josh Sneed";
  schema:description "Josh Sneed has been on Last Comic Standing, Comedy Central and is one of the most played comedians on Sirius X/M radio. His sharp wit brought gales of laughter to Montreal's Just For Laughs Festival, The Aspen Comedy Festival and the South Beach Comedy Festival. iTunes selected his comedy Album \"Unacceptable\"as one of the Top 10 comedy albums of the year. Josh was a regular on The Bob & Tom radio show, and has appeared with Dave Chappelle, Jim Gaffigan and Kevin Hart. Check out his Dry Bar Comedy special Josh Sneed: Live in the Dessert.";
