iwts_performer:10217 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Mike Williams on Sax";
  schema:description "Mike Williams on Sax is a Billboard Charting & Inspirational Saxophonist, with influences of Smooth Jazz, R&B, Pop, Oldies, Funk, Fusion, Indie Rock, and Gospel. Mike is originally from Cincinnati, Ohio, but has called North-West Ohio; particularly Greater Toledo, home for the past 12 years. He loves cross generational music; and the blending of various musical genres and styles. With 20 years of experience in live entertainment and performance; Mike has acquired knowledge in a wide variety of different types of stages and performance spaces.";
