  schema:name "The Life and Times of Jim Croce";
  schema:description "The Life and Times of Jim Croce is a carefully curated show performing the hits and deep cuts of legendary 70's icon Jim Croce. With three lead singers and over 80 years of on stage experience combined this outfit is a true and authentic tribute to the revered songwriter. In 2025 this show took on 22 theatre stages across the prairies selling over 3,500 tickets as an independent group.";
