iwts_performer:10227 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Sukanya Chand";
  schema:description """Sukanya Chand is a performer, a choreographer, and a teacher, who specializes in Bharatanatyam and Odissi dances from India. Her work has been presented at festivals, schools, and universities, reflecting a thoughtful balance of tradition and innovation. She is the founder of Natya Nirvana, that was established to enrich the Central Ohio community through arts education. Sukanya brings classical Indian dance to life both on stage and in the classroom and is an instructor at MUCAI Academy in Worthington, Ohio.
Facebook & Instagram: Natya Nirvana""";
