  schema:name "Kayla Williams";
  schema:description "Kayla Williams is a Calgary-based yacht-pop artist blending soulful vocals with the warmth and groove of ’70s and ’80s soft rock. Inspired by artists like Hall & Oates and Fleetwood Mac, her music pairs nostalgic sounds with a modern pop sensibility. Her EP RETRODELIA earned Western Canadian Music Award and YYC Music Award recognition, and her latest release POPSTALGIA showcases a bold, playful evolution. Williams performs with her high-energy band, The Yacht Daddies, delivering vibrant live shows across Western Canada.";
