iwts_performer:10238 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Bel and Quinn";
  schema:description "JUNO-nominated duo Bel and Quinn has crafted an electrifying musical world that blends jazz, soul, and konpa from Haiti. Bel writes the lyrics, while Quinn composes and arranges the music, showcasing her skills as a jazz guitarist. The two sisters of Haitian descent released their critically acclaimed debut album, “Donte sann yo”, in October 2023, singing in French, Creole, and English. Their messages of self-acceptance and healing deeply resonate with listeners. They are advocates for women in music and perform with a talented four-piece band.";
