  schema:description "2025 NC Heritage Award Winner Gaurang Doshi is an performing artist, composer, educator, and author performing Indian Classical Music on the string instrument Sarod as per the traditions of the \"Maihar Gharana\". Gaurang learned from his father and Guru Pandit Dr. Laxmikant Doshi who was India's leading Sarod Maestro. Gaurang performs ONLY in concert halls where people do not eat and drink while he performs. Details about his work can be seen on his website www.SarodSitar.com";
