iwts_performer:10262 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Duncan Cox";
  schema:description """Duncan Cox is an Actor/Musician from Winnipeg, Manitoba. His work writing for musical theatre productions has greatly informed his emphasis on intentional clarity, honest delivery, and narrative structures in his music. His work stems from a background centred in raw acoustic Folk/Celtic rock and a mix of both guttural and gentle storytelling. 
Duncan's art holds up the three \"hues\": humility, humanity, and humour, and he employs all of them to best connect with his audiences, from the very young through to those nearing expiry.""";
