  schema:description "Dr. Daniel Tselyakov is a Canadian concert pianist acclaimed for extraordinary virtuosity, emotional intensity, and profound interpretive depth. A soloist with the Winnipeg Symphony Orchestra and internationally across North America and Europe, he has appeared at major festivals and venues including the Kennedy Center. Praised for bold, compelling performances and rare artistic insight, he is Artistic Director of the Clear Lake Chamber Music Festival and a member of the academic staff at Brandon University.";
  schema:url <https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AGyFDDK9EBY>;
  schema:knowsAbout <http://kg.artsdata.ca/resource/MusicPerformance>;
