iwts_performer:10266 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Mellow Lily";
  schema:description """Mellow Lily is more than just a voice-she's a force.
A gifted singer-songwriter from Kingston, she has 17 years of experience in the industry. Her performances are woven with the depth of someone who lives and breathes music.
In 2024, she signed a distribution deal with Radar Love Records, and 
She’s shared the stage with Grammy nominees Della Mae, Canadian blues star Crystal Shawanda, and Canadian Folk Music Award winner Abigail Lapell.
• Come see why Mellow Lily is one of the most exciting musical acts on the rise.""";
