iwts_performer:10275 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Billy Raffoul";
  schema:description """Billy Raffoul is an award-winning singer, songwriter, and producer based in Ontario. Hailing from
Leamington, he followed in the footsteps of his father, professional musician Jody Raffoul. His music blends riff-powered rock ‘n’ roll and brutally honest acoustic confessionals. His most recent full length albums, Billy Raffoul & When I Cross The River, were released four weeks apart in 2025. Billy has amassed over 500 million total streams and received praise across various publications including Billboard, American Songwriter, Paste, and more.""";
