  schema:name "The Silver Starlets";
  schema:description "The Silver Starlets started in 2015 at the Edmonton International Fringe Festival. Since then, this Canadian duo has performed around the world at children's festivals, fairs, street festivals & special events. Performance highlights include the World Buskers Festival & Auckland International Busker Festival (New Zealand), The Pacific National Exhibition (Vancouver), Winnipeg Children's Festival, Ottawa International Busker Festival, and The Dubai Shopping Festival.";
