  schema:name "The Sistering";
  schema:description "The Sistering unites four acclaimed vocalists—Lois Deloatch, Nnenna Freelon, Lenora Zenzalai Helm, and Kate McGarry—in a powerful musical collective rooted in sisterhood and shared truth. Blending jazz, gospel, folk, and ballads, their original songs explore love, loss, and resilience with raw honesty and rich harmony. More than a performance, The Sistering is an intimate, soul-stirring experience of connection, creativity, and collective strength.";
