  schema:name "Plus Dueling Pianos";
  schema:description "Plus Dueling Pianos – The Road Show delivers a high-energy, fully interactive live music experience that transforms theaters into unforgettable events. Blending top-tier musicianship with fast-paced comedy, our all-request format puts the audience in control—creating a unique, crowd-driven show every time. With dynamic lighting, powerful sound, and nonstop engagement, this isn’t just a performance—it’s an experience.";
