  schema:name "Kala'e + Kalena";
  schema:description "Kala‘e + Kalena, premier Hawaiian country duo, combines the talents of award-winning husband and wife, sharing joyous energy, stunning harmonies and an infectious chemistry that delights audiences. Seasoned entertainers with roots in the vibrant landscapes of Hawai‘i Island, their performances offer a lively mix of high-energy country classics, soul-stirring originals, powerful ballads, and rich Hawaiian tradition. “Native Hawaiian country music? Consider your horizons expanded.” (Grammy.com). The spirit of country with the aloha of Hawai’i.";
