iwts_performer:10294 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Zach Freidhof";
  schema:description """Troubadour of Peace
An uplifting blend of folk & soul immersed in Love.

In 1997, a case of appendicitis brought Zach to the brink of death. In that moment, Zach was inspired &compelled to bring music into the world. “It felt like I was picked up &put on my path, & so music & performance feel like a sacred gift I get to honor & share.”

Over 5,000 performances later, spanning North America, 43 records written, recorded & released, Zach is still sharing &honoring that gift of music. He’s been awarded the John T. Looney Award for Justice & Peace.""";
  schema:url <https://zachmusic.love>;
  schema:knowsAbout <http://kg.artsdata.ca/resource/MusicPerformance>;
