iwts_performer:10295 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Mo-Grass";
  schema:description """Mo-Grass is an all-star North Carolina collective that brings classic Motown and soul reimagined with the energy and charm of bluegrass. 
Blending bluegrass traditions with electric guitars and soulful vocals, Mo-Grass transforms timeless hits into something fresh, joyful, and unforgettable.
Drawing from a legendary catalog, Mo-Grass performs beloved songs by artists like Stevie Wonder, The Temptations, Otis Redding, The Isley Brothers, Sam Cooke, Marvin Gaye, and many more
This is a brand new project, so we don't have a website built yet.""";
