  schema:description """Motel 5 is a new group of award winning Northwest vocal and instrumental artists, with a fresh Americana sound. Joe Vinikow, Julie Sakahara, and Julian Smedley showcase their eclectic Nashville recordings, from retro Honky Tonk and Western swing, to a strong helping of jazz and roots R&B. 

