iwts_performer:10303 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Hayde";
  schema:description "Hayde Bluegrass Orchestra is a Norwegian band blending American bluegrass with Nordic folk influences. The band gained international recognition with their debut album Migrants, which reached #4 on the Billboard Bluegrass chart and was nominated for the Norwegian Grammy \"Spelemannsprisen\". Vocalist Rebekka Nilsson won IBMA Momentum Vocalist of the Year, and the band was nominated for Band of the Year.  Hayde has toured extensively in the US and Europe, performing at major festivals and venues.";
