iwts_performer:10304 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Carolina Pine";
  schema:description """Blending the golden era of country with the intimacy of American folk, Carolina Pine delivers a timeless, harmony-rich performance inspired by the sounds of Merle Haggard, Emmylou Harris, Johnny Cash, and Gillian Welch.

They have toured nationally as an opening act for Alan Jackson, earned a #1 song for six consecutive weeks on Bluegrass Music TV, and built a devoted following with millions of views online. Now, with their debut full-length album in the works, Carolina Pine is bringing a fresh voice to a timeless tradition.""";
