iwts_performer:10318 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Legend of the Pioneers";
  schema:description """Legend of The Pioneers 

Throughout the years there have been many pioneers in the field of entertainment. The Legend of the Pioneers' show is packed with stories and songs from entertainers in several genres of music and film.  From the Silver Screen Cowboys to Western Swing, Classic Country, Pop and some good ol' Rock and Roll. Recognizable songs that make the audience sing along. 

The life and times of the legendary entertainment icons - all told in story and song with incredible three-part harmony. And wrapped in rhinestones.""";
