iwts_performer:10320 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Carla Cerceau";
  schema:description """Carla Cerceau is a celebrated aerial artist, choreographer, and entertainer with over a decade of experience captivating audiences through the power of movement, comedy, and flight. 
Carla brings a signature blend of elegance, athleticism, and theatricality to every performance and production.
Based in Winnipeg, Manitoba, Carla has performed on some of the city's most iconic stages. Her specialties include aerial hoop, aerial silks, hand balancing, fire manipulation, partner acrobatics, and juggling, making her a true multidisciplinary artist.""";
