  schema:name "Aint Sisters";
  schema:description """Aint Sisters is an Atlanta-based, female-fronted rock band delivering a powerful blend of emotional intensity, tight harmonies, and genre-traveling songwriting. Fronted by Barb Carbon and Arrie Bozeman, and backed by Justin Boudreau (bass) and Richie Jones (drums), the band has built a reputation for fiery, electric live performances that pull audiences in and keep them coming back. 
 Their diverse sound draws in fans of artists like the Billy Strings, Larkin Poe, Daniel Donato, Indigo Girls, Brandi Carlile, and Tedeschi Trucks Band.""";
