  schema:description """America’s Master Mentalist. Storyteller. Relational Guide.
Jon Stetson has spent a lifetime studying how people think, decide, and connect. As the real-life inspiration for the hit CBS series The Mentalist, Jon brings a rare combination of observational psychology, mastery of human behavior, and live demonstrations to audiences around the world.
While his demonstrations are extraordinary, they are always handled with respect, professionalism, and care – creating an environment where trust forms quickly and engagement runs deep.""";
