  schema:name "THE EDGE EFFECT";
  schema:description """THE EDGE EFFECT - Danny Alan, Troy Dolendo, Sean Gerrity, John Gibson II, and Karl Hudson - is a five-man vocal band dedicated to great music with NO Autotune. Formed in 2011, the \"America's Got Talent\" finalists offer a diverse, decade-spanning sound.

