iwts_performer:10328 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Delnora";
  schema:description "Delnora is a multi-award winning singer/songwriter based near Nashville, Tennessee. The WV native has been performing her signature blend of roots, country and folk music across the country since she was a teenager, continuing a long and distinguished family tradition in music. Delnora was recently named the 2026 ICMA Female Vocalist of the Year at the Grand Ole Opry, where she also performed. She has written and released several #1 songs, and her latest single \"Looking For The Light\" debuted earlier this month on the legendary WSM Nashville.";
