  schema:name "Sunnyside Stringband";
  schema:description "Sunnyside Stringband is an up-and-coming collaboration of top notch pickers born out of the musical community in Asheville, NC. Floirda-born songstress, Sunnie Rae sews her songs in the fertile soils of Appalachia. Her new band thrives to bring life to her Original Music and Timeless Covers. This super-string ensemble bends and mends the genre-fitting confinements, playing each tune to its own. Feel the depth of every song with Sunnie Rae’s intrinsic voice that will take you on a timeless journey.";
