  schema:name "Evening Star";
  schema:description """Evening Star is an afro-futuristic odyssey led by Detroit drummer Tariq Gardner, blending the city’s rich jazz legacy with neo-soul, hip-hop, Afro-Cuban, and Black American music traditions. Their sound merges the roots of the Motherland with cosmic exploration, creating music as a positive and transformative force.
Born from Detroit’s expansive and genre-bending music scene, Evening Star is a sonic journey through the galaxies of the African Diaspora.""";
