iwts_performer:10356 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Kylie Fox";
  schema:description "Kylie Fox is a Canadiana queen, a free-spirited songbird, and a tree-hugging feminist. Her brand of Americana blends humour, wit, and 70s glitz to tell stories rooted in Canadian culture. She’s inspired by the whimsy of Jenny Lewis, the lyricism of Joni Mitchell and the showmanship of Brandi Carlile. She’s currently working on a new record, slated for release in the Fall of 2026.";
