  schema:name "dave eggar";
  schema:description "Hailing from the birthplace of country music, Bristol Lightning's powerful blend of Bluegrass, storytelling, blues and classical composer like Aaron Copland and Florence Price, celebrates the last 100 years of Americas music in powerful evenings that' cross stylistic barriers. They have performed festivals nationwide and have appeared with symphony orchestra and led education workshops";
