iwts_performer:10368 a schema:Organization;
  schema:name "The Bear in the Backyard";
  schema:description """Bear in the Backyard follows Dusty as they try to rid their backyard of a pesky Bear that is getting into their garbage and wrecking their fruit trees. Joined by their neighbors Turk and Bell, caos  ensues when the Bear,  Fish and Wildlife and the squirrels get involved. 
Written by Tyler Olsen of Theater 825, and performed by the Playhouse Ensemble; Evan Grande, Victoria Timoteo and Alex Hilses,  Bear in the Backyard  features shadow puppetry, squirrels. physical comedy, costume changes and music.""";
