  schema:name "The Do Lollies";
  schema:description "The Do Lollies bring vintage jazz and swing to life with warm harmonies, playful charm, and an inviting stage presence. Inspired by the sounds of the 1920s and 30s, their performances feel like stepping into another era while remaining fresh, joyful, and accessible to modern audiences. Equally suited for concert settings, festivals, community events, and social gatherings, they create memorable experiences that draw audiences in.";
