  schema:name "Sharptail";
  schema:description "Sharptail blends fiddle, banjo, and guitar to tell stories of love, adventure, and human struggle. Their raw, emotional sound draws listeners into intimate performances rooted in Saskatchewan folk traditions. Formed by Aryn Murray and Mitch Dureault, their music reflects community roots and explores healing, mental health, and creating safe spaces for unheard voices.";
