iwts_performer:10378 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Donny Parenteau";
  schema:description "Donny Parenteau, Carmen Robertson and Ed Sinclair are longtime friends who have talked about putting together a show for more then a decade. It's finally come to a reality, where they bring your favorites from the 70's and 80's (country and rock) together for an evening of singing, dancing and reminiscing. With Donny's music career spanning 40 years from playing fiddle with Neal McCoy to his own solo career leading him to 3 Juno nominations you will see what all those years next to his friends can do to entertain you.";
