  schema:name "Sydney Hair";
  schema:description """Minor Paradox lead singer, Sydney Hair wows audiences with her stratospheric vocal range. Her tone can go from smooth and silky to rocky road grit at will. She started professionally singing in 2014 when she was just 15 years old.
