  schema:name "Black Umfolosi International";
  schema:description "Black Umfolosi International is a group that performs Southern African acapella music known as Imbube. It's a spectacular combination of harmonies accompanied by rhythmic melodies and dance movements that wow audiences everywhere.  The group is also visually appealing as the performers showcase the traditional Southern African attire. It's a show not to miss!";
