iwts_performer:10384 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Ryan Joyce";
  schema:description """Ryan Joyce: Magician & Comedy Hypnotist. Two Shows. One Unforgettable Result.

With 13 national tours and 6,000+ shows in 80 countries, Ryan is a proven PAC headliner. As seen on Penn & Teller: Fool Us, he offers two distinct productions: a grand-scale Magic & Illusion spectacle and a sophisticated Comedy Hypnosis experience. 

Both feature hilarious interaction and technical ease, designed to bring the WOW factor to every seat in the house. “Damn impressive!” — Martin Short. 

A true master of modern variety.""";
